{
  "name": "200 - Ransomware Intelligence Platform (Advanced IOC Enrichment + YARA + Multi-Channel)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "2942bc37-47d8-430d-bdf7-a95b6806bfa5",
      "name": "README",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -200,
        -400
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## \ud83d\udd34 Level 200 \u2014 Advanced Ransomware Intelligence Platform\n\n### What's New vs 101\n- **IOC Enrichment**: VirusTotal + AbuseIPDB lookups on victim domains/IPs\n- **YARA Rule Generation**: AI generates detection rules per threat group\n- **Historical Trending**: Compares current period vs prior 30-day baseline\n- **Multi-Channel Delivery**: Slack + Email + Webhook\n- **Automated Ticketing**: Creates JIRA/ServiceNow tickets for P1 threats\n- **Confidence Scoring**: Multi-signal weighted attribution score\n\n### Prerequisites\n- VirusTotal API key (free tier: 500 req/day)\n- AbuseIPDB API key (free tier available)\n- SMTP or SendGrid for email\n- Optional: JIRA/ServiceNow credentials",
        "height": 450,
        "width": 500,
        "color": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7cb997f0-ff9b-4a25-b7e8-f95ab5c5e7db",
      "name": "Every 6 Hours",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        0,
        0
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "hours",
              "triggerAtHour": 0,
              "hoursInterval": 6
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "370740bc-6ade-4686-b0d1-f7189571ceca",
      "name": "Fetch Recent Victims",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
