    {
      "id": "2abc9eba-0881-4651-ae4e-a717beec5755",
      "name": "200 Architecture",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        -300
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 200-Level Workflow Architecture\n\n**New Capabilities:**\n1. **IOC Enrichment** \u2014 VT + AbuseIPDB lookups\n2. **YARA Rule Generation** \u2014 AI-generated per-group rules\n3. **Historical Trending** \u2014 30d vs prior 30d comparison  \n4. **Multi-Channel Delivery** \u2014 Slack + Email + JIRA + Google Docs\n5. **Confidence Scoring** \u2014 0-100% attribution confidence\n6. **Negotiation Intelligence** \u2014 Demand ranges and decryptor info\n\n**Data Flow:**\nSchedule \u2192 API Fetch \u2192 IOC Extract \u2192 Enrich \u2192 AI Analysis (+ YARA) \u2192 HTML + YARA File \u2192 All Outputs",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 480,
        "color": 3
      }
    }
